Reed De Rouen https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Reed_De_Rouen 0 Reed De Rouen (10 June 1917 – 11 June 1986) was an American actor and screenwriter who worked mostly in the British film and television industry. He appeared in the Doctor Who serial The Gunfighters in 1966 as Pa Clanton, as well as writing the script for the proposed Doctor Who story "The Spare Part People" with Jon Pertwee.
